#

Grilled Shrimp Skewers with Lemon and Garlic

25 min
$12
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickGrilledSeafood

Description

Tender shrimp marinated in zesty lemon and garlic, grilled to perfection for a quick and flavorful meal.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • lemon (juiced): 1
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • skewers (wooden or metal): 4-6
